---
---

<section class="bg-[#FFFDF1] py-[80px] px-[20px] font-['DM_Sans',sans-serif]">
  <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row items-stretch bg-white rounded-[8px] overflow-hidden shadow-[0_4px_20px_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)]">

    <!-- Image -->
    <div class="flex-1 self-stretch min-h-[300px] md:min-h-[500px] w-full">
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556761175-b413da4baf72?w=800&h=600&fit=crop"
        alt="Team collaboration"
        class="block w-full h-full object-cover"
      >
    </div>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="flex-1 p-[40px] md:p-[60px]">
      <div class="inline-block border-[2px] border-black px-[16px] py-[8px] text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[1px] mb-[24px] uppercase">
        YOUR TRUSTED DENVER MARKETING PARTNERS
      </div>
      <h2 class="font-['Playfair_Display',serif] text-[28px] md:text-[36px] leading-[1.2] mb-[20px] text-black font-bold">
        WHY DENVER BUSINESSES CHOOSE OUR MARKETING PROS
      </h2>
      <p class="text-[#333] leading-[1.8] mb-[32px] text-[16px]">
        We're not just another agency. We're <strong>Denver marketing pros</strong> and locals who
        understand the market, know the neighborhoods, and have the relationships that get
        results. Our clients choose us because we deliver measurable outcomes, transparent
        reporting, and personalized service that treats your business like our own. From <strong>web
        design to PPC campaigns</strong>, we've got you covered.
      </p>
      <button class="px-[32px] py-[14px] bg-transparent border-[2px] border-black text-black font-semibold text-[14px] tracking-[0.5px] cursor-pointer transition-all duration-300 uppercase hover:bg-black hover:text-[#FFFDF1]">
        GET STARTED TODAY
      </button>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>